                                    Perfect Rooms, Perfect Prices.
                                

                                    Station Casinos operates the widest selection of hotels in Las Vegas, with 10 distinct hotel and casino properties and over 4,000 affordable hotel rooms. Our off the strip hotel properties feature rooms for every taste, style and budget. Whether you’re looking for a luxury suite with mountain views, or a comfortable, yet affordable room just off the world-famous Strip, we’re prepared to put you up in style.
                                

Learn More










                                    Incredible Entertainment 
                                

                                    Our 10 hotel and casino properties feature more entertainment options than anyone else in Las Vegas. From the very best rock, country, blues and jazz concerts to luxurious nightclubs and lounges, friendly bars and hilarious comedy acts, we’ve got something for everyone, no matter what kind of mood they’re in. Our family friendly hotels are ready to please children of all ages, featuring on-site movie theaters, bowling centers, arcades, and supervised child care centers. We’re sure you’ll agree that Station Casinos offers the best entertainment in Las Vegas.


Learn More










                                    The Most Gaming Choices
                                

                                    Featuring 24,000 of your favorite casino games across our network of casino hotel properties, Station Casinos offers the best gambling in Las Vegas. Whether you like slots, video poker, table games, live poker, keno, bingo, sports betting or horseracing, you’ll find that and more at our exciting Las Vegas casinos. With better odds, higher payouts and more gambling excitement than you’ll find on the Strip, there’s no wonder why we’re known as the locals’ favorite gaming destination.


                                

Learn More










                                    Best of Las Vegas Dining 
                                

                                    Where should you look for the best restaurants in Las Vegas? It’s simple: Station Casinos. Our restaurants have received more than 100 “Best of Las Vegas” awards from the Las Vegas Review-Journal, and for good reason – they’re fantastic! Whether you’re in the mood for a fine dining experience or a casual meal, you’ll be able to find that and much more at one of our Las Vegas Hotels & Casinos. Featuring authentic Italian cuisine, modern Japanese meals, fresh Mexican food and the best steakhouses and seafood restaurants in Sin City, we’ve got something to please every palate.
                                

Learn More










                                    Award-Winning Spas
                                

                                    When it comes time to nourish your mind, body and spirit, you can rest assured that the Station Casinos Spas are ready to serve. Treat yourself to a relaxing, rejuvenating spa experience like no other at either of our award-winning “Best of Las Vegas” Spas – The Spa at Red Rock Resort or The Spa at Green Valley Ranch. Our Spas offer state-of-the-art facilities, luxurious surroundings and an extensive menu of holistic treatments, including massages, facials, body treatments, spa fitness packages and salon services.
                                

Learn More










                                    Meeting Space & Special Events 
                                

No one hosts Las Vegas meetings better than Station Casinos. Our network of 10 hotel and casino properties ensures that you’ll be able to find the perfect setting for your corporate event, wedding, or private party. Additionally, our experienced event-planning and catering professionals are prepared to turn your event into an effortless, unforgettable evening. Featuring a variety of spaces, from intimate meeting rooms to elegant banquet facilities, we’re able to accommodate groups as small as a few dozen or as large as a few thousand. Each meeting space is configurable, and can be tailored to fit your group’s needs and budget. Whether you want to host an intimate networking affair, or a major corporate or social convention, no place serves as a better host than Station Casinos.

Learn More










