                    Santa Fe Station Hotel & Casino
                

                    Santa Fe Station is conveniently located in Northwest Las Vegas, mere minutes away from the action-packed Las Vegas Strip, stunning Red Rock Canyon National Conservation Area, and Las Vegas’ top local skiing and snowboarding destination, Mt. Charleston. Featuring comfortable, yet affordable bedrooms, modern accommodations and a generous selection of restaurants, Santa Fe offers everything you need for an outstanding Las Vegas vacation.
Learn More

